# Internal scratch — NOT committed.
# Note: `docs/` is intentionally NOT excluded — it is the load-bearing
# artifact directory (architecture.md, design_decisions.md,
# evaluation_methodology.md, ablations.md, trust_calibration.md,
# parser_benchmark.md, report.md, test_inventory.md). The plan's value
# proposition depends on these being reviewable on the public repo.
progress.txt
.scratch/

# Run-logger artifacts (M2). Per the plan §3.1:
#   - manifest.json, summary.json, report.md, per_example.json — COMMITTED
#   - raw per-request logs — gitignored (can be megabytes per run)
data/runs/*/raw_responses.jsonl
data/runs/*/prompts.jsonl
data/runs/*/request_log.jsonl
data/runs/*/checkpoint.json

